Package: hansardR
Type: Package
Title: Process Australian Parliamentary Hansard Data from a gazillion csv files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kenneth", "Benoit", email = "kbenoit@smu.edu.sg", role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0797-564X"))
  )
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for processing, validating, and analysing 
    Australian Parliamentary Hansard CSV data. Provides functions for database 
    creation, file validation, batch processing, and structured queries of 
    parliamentary speeches, debates, and member information.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
